window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A simple arrangement. A complicated future.</b></p> <p>Lia Dove has always been a free spirit, living life to the fullest, and never putting down roots. But, after finding her birth father - along with a group of lovable, rowdy bikers - she can’t imagine being anywhere else. Throw in a hot biker roommate, who offers her a no-strings-attached deal as the cherry on top, and leaving becomes an afterthought.</p> <p>Leo Hawk has never felt part of anything, until he becomes a prospect at a local motorcycle club. But catching feelings for his roommate, who’s also the club president’s daughter, could spell disaster before he earns his patch.</p> <p>And when the past comes back to haunt him, thanks to his missing older brother, Leo will have to lean on his biker brothers for help - risking a future with the club, and the woman he’s grown to love.</p> <p><i>Broken Dove </i>is an interconnected, standalone, friends-to-lovers, motorcycle club romance - but it can be read and enjoyed alone.</p>"; 
